## Phase 3: Analysis
- [ ] Migration completeness per branch
- [ ] Functional preservation per branch
- [ ] Scope discipline per branch
- [ ] Correctness of PF-specific migration per branch
- [ ] Build/compile results per branch
- [ ] Risk/maintainability per branch

## Phase 4: Report
- [ ] Score all branches
- [ ] Generate HTML report
- [ ] Save to project root


