    content: 
# PatternFly 5→6 Migration Comparison Report

## Phase 1: Research ✅
- [x] Research PF6 migration guide and breaking changes
- [x] Build migration checklist from official docs

## Phase 2: Baseline ✅
- [x] Identify branches and get basic stats
- [x] Get diffs for each migration branch vs main
- [x] Attempt builds on each branch

## Phase 3: Analysis ✅
- [x] Migration completeness per branch
- [x] Functional preservation per branch
- [x] Scope discipline per branch
- [x] Correctness of PF-specific migration per branch
- [x] Build/compile results per branch
- [x] Risk/maintainability per branch

## Phase 4: Report
- [ ] Score all branches
- [ ] Generate HTML report
- [ ] Save to project root

## KEY FINDINGS:
### Branch 1 (pf-codemods-053026-2011): 23 files, +163/-60
- Focused: Only ModalVariant -> deprecated import path
- Zero new TS errors vs main
- Codemod artifact: 'constructor' -> 'function Object() { [native code] }' in eslint config
- Added .cache file (junk)
- No package.json changes
- No CSS/SCSS changes
- Missed: Icon wrapper, SelectList, InputGroupItem, CSS tokens, charts, etc.

### Branch 2 (semver/goose/053026-1839): 165 files, +1252/-1206
- Broad changes: Icon removal, SelectList, DescriptionListGroup, InputGroupItem, Tbody, CSS pf-v5->pf-v6
- 16 new TS errors (charts/victory imports, react-i18next downgrade)
- CRITICAL BUG: ~88 component= prop misuses (StackItem/SplitItem children moved to component prop)
- BAD package.json: react-charts downgraded 8.4.0->6.2.3, react 17->18, react-router-dom 5->7, react-i18next 11->2.2.3, eslint nonsensical range
- Did NOT move ModalVariant to deprecated
- Good: CSS token pf-v5->pf-v6, Icon wrapper removal, test selector updates


