<!-- ==================== 3. BRANCH OVERVIEW ==================== -->
<h2 id="overview">Branch Overview</h2>
<p>Base branch: <code>main</code> — already has PF6 package versions in package.json (6.4.0) with react-charts 8.4.0. The codebase is partially migrated: it uses composable Modal patterns (ModalHeader/ModalBody/ModalFooter) but still imports <code>ModalVariant</code> from <code>@patternfly/react-core</code> instead of <code>@patternfly/react-core/deprecated</code>. It retains <code>pf-c-</code> CSS class references, <code>&lt;Icon&gt;</code> wrapper patterns, and uses <code>@patternfly/react-charts/victory</code> imports. Pre-existing: 21 TypeScript errors (OvaVM type drift, useLightspeed, i18n).</p>

